==English==
===Noun===
'''release candidate'''

# This [[development status]] is given to a [[program]] or [[application]] that is basically the final product, but there may still be a few bugs lurking in the [[program]]. Often this status is reffered to as [[delta]] (maybe even [[gamma]], or more [[Greek]] letters. Also, this status may be split into one other called [[omega]] where it is the final product, but it could go into development at any time. This status comes after [[beta version]], and is before the [[release version]].

